videos.description: Gordon Hayward finds a cutting Cody Zeller who goes up to pound down a dunk with authority in the lane.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Hayward hooks up with Zeller for a dunk) 2021/03/18 ESHEET

videos.headline: Hayward hooks up with Zeller for a dunk

videos.description: LeBron James gets the full-court outlet pass from Markieff Morris and goes up to throw down a two-handed dunk to cap the Lakers' fast break.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (LeBron flushes early fast-break dunk) 2021/03/18 ESHEET

videos.headline: LeBron flushes early fast-break dunk

videos.description: LaMelo Ball beats Markieff Morris and goes up to put in a sweet reverse layup in transition for the Hornets.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (LaMelo scores on saucy reverse) 2021/03/18 ESHEET

videos.headline: LaMelo scores on saucy reverse

videos.description: LeBron James uses a step-back move to get to the corner and fades out of bounds to sink a 3-pointer against Cody Zeller.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (LeBron cashes out fadeaway step-back 3 in the corner) 2021/03/18 ESHEET

videos.headline: LeBron cashes out fadeaway step-back 3 in the corner

videos.description: LeBron James uses a spin move on the fast break to navigate through three defenders and go up for a smooth layup.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (LeBron spins on 3 defenders for fast-break bucket) 2021/03/18 ESHEET

videos.headline: LeBron spins on 3 defenders for fast-break bucket

videos.description: Wes Matthews comes away with the steal and Talen Horton-Tucker tosses a lob to LeBron James for the fast-break slam.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (THT sets up LeBron for alley-oop slam) 2021/03/18 ESHEET

videos.headline: THT sets up LeBron for alley-oop slam

videos.description: Kyle Kuzma throws a flashy pass to LeBron James to throw down a powerful fast-break slam for the Lakers.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Kuzma sets up LeBron for emphatic slam) 2021/03/18 ESHEET

videos.headline: Kuzma sets up LeBron for emphatic slam

videos.description: The Lakers held a moment of silence prior to their game against the Hornets in support of the Asian and Pacific Islander communities and to honor the victims of Tuesday's shootings in the Atlanta area.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Lakers hold moment of silence honoring victims of Tuesday's Atlanta-area shootings) 2021/03/18 ESHEET

videos.headline: Lakers hold moment of silence honoring victims of Tuesday's Atlanta-area shootings

videos.description: Miles Bridges elevates to catch the lob from Devonte' Graham and flushes the alley-oop with Kyle Kuzma all on his back.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Bridges goes up to flush alley-oop jam) 2021/03/18 ESHEET

videos.headline: Bridges goes up to flush alley-oop jam

videos.description: LeBron James turns around in confusion because he doesn't get a call after he leans in to draw a foul as he knocks down a 3-pointer.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (LeBron confused after no foul is called on his 3) 2021/03/18 ESHEET

videos.headline: LeBron confused after no foul is called on his 3

videos.description: LeBron James gets beat off the dribble by Terry Rozier, but he quickly recovers and swats away Rozier's layup attempt with ferocity.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (LeBron recovers to make spectacular block) 2021/03/18 ESHEET

videos.headline: LeBron recovers to make spectacular block

videos.description: LeBron James gives his take on the MVP award and thinks he "should have more than four" MVPs.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Presser (LeBron: 'I should have more than 4' MVPs) 2021/03/19

videos.headline: LeBron: 'I should have more than 4' MVPs
